{"tid":135024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涂謹申：只立辱警罪唔立辱民罪 市民咪更加㷫？","createTime":"2017-02-26T04:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T02:40:09.000Z","uid":48093,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"075b4fc7206eba15d6dc91dfd24480bed60f1bac","tid":135024,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488081276_5076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488081276_5076.jpg&h=05cad63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察協會早前舉行「會員大會」撐七警，更聲言要求就「辱警罪」立法。立法會保安事務委員會副主席涂謹申出席無綫節目《講清講楚》時說，擔心就設立「辱警罪」，會對社會造成更大撕裂，「如果你立『辱警罪』，而唔立『辱民罪』，市民咪就更加㷫？&hellip;&hellip;我覺得對警察都不利嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申說，難以界定「辱警罪」的內容，且在現時的社會背景氣氛下，很難平心靜氣討論。<br />\n對於現時警民關係緊張，涂指雙方要多溝通才可解決矛盾，作為民主派的議員，亦會呼籲市民尊重警察。他說，作為市民可行使和平集會的權利，警察都肯定市民的權利、安排，但雙方有時有些虛位、灰色地帶，究竟應該容許市民走多近，警方又會擔心市民影響到嘉賓，「其實係嗰個虛位，其實大家多啲有商有量，討論先至得」。"},{"pid":"bffc4b2446e78e7485e717101492096393cb4c3f","tid":135024,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1a74c795c909dfcfdf294badc34b101d46a432","tid":135024,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f82c80693a61914fb69a376228959641be064e4","tid":135024,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"其實市民好簡單，合理就撐唔合理<br />\n當年amina摑一巴個個知你差佬做戲都撐你，今日個個屌柒你就知有幾柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9d500e17e59e1ea15f25bcf9c55083ca7e6858","tid":135024,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"有涂謹申，掂啦今次"},{"pid":"12283b971f1fe41a17d2a6a83fb08fda2f33847c","tid":135024,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"立辱警罪根本係多餘<br />\n人地係心或私底下背反辱罵你 <br />\n睇你唔起 當你地係xxx<br />\n見到你地細細聲同人講<br />\n&quot;睇吓 正一係xxxxx&quot;<br />\n你又拉人告人？！"},{"pid":"d30397642f190e195536ae8158f4e194975d31ea","tid":135024,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12906446109d30e4d200a30aaf5777977a0e1c8f","tid":135024,"uid":39572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a113d6d767b98a5109d35250e65fc898a3a3233","tid":135024,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab02191b5bc0a674dc9b1fb4bb735e7d37b0fb95","tid":135024,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實市民好簡單，合理就撐唔合理<br />\n當年amina摑一巴個個知你差佬做戲都撐你，今日個個屌柒你就知有幾柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撐撚錯左 amina 如果係兩年咁做一定做英雄"}]}